Extra Virgin Americana - Season 1, Episode 8




Motor City Deb-olition Derby

Debi Mazar loves Motown, classic cars and American history, so its only fitting that she, Gabriele Corcos and their family stop in Detroit. They take a tour of the Model T plant, where Debi takes the original classic car out for a spin, and the family cooks up a tailgating feast to share with new friends while Gabriele competes in a real demolition derby!




Original Air Date: 20-Apr-2016
